it.polimi.deib.se2019.sanp4.adrenaline.common.network.socket

Interface SocketClientCommand

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoginResponse, PerformRequestCommand, PingCommand, SelectSceneCommand, ShowMessageCommand, UpdateCommand

    public interface SocketClientCommand
    Represents a command that a server wants to issue on a client communicating with Socket. The target of this command is SocketClientCommandTarget, usually a SocketServerConnection residing on the client
    Author:
    Alessandro Fulgini
